<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="Aink302">
<l>arumporuḷ ceyviṉai tappaṟku murittē</l>
<l>peruntō ḷarivai takaittaṟku muriyaḷ</l>
<l>cellā yāyiṉō naṉṟē</l>
<l>mellam pulampa vivaḷaḻap pirintē</l>
      </lg>
  <lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">
<l>Efforts made for [gaining] precious wealth may fail.</l>
<l>And woman with plumpy shoulders is likely to be afflicted.</l>
<l>Man from the calm beautiful seashore! </l>
<l>It will be good, if you don’t go away, making her weep in separation.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
